      <title>中国电动汽车制造商对欧盟的冷淡回应在关税争端中付出了高昂代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/china-ev-maker-s-tepid-reply-to-eu-proves-costly-in-tariff-spat</link>
